1.09_02 22 Jun 2007  DEVELOPER RELEASE
                     Added advanced usage options:
                      - skip
                      - is_local
                      - load_as
                      - sort
                      - debug
                      - array overrides

                      Fixed a bug (reported by Ewan Edwards) where
                      an array exists in the main config and a hash in
                      the local override

